   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Vonpar Alimentos</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC&apos;s investment in Vonpar will have a direct and significant impact in the region&apos;s development:  (i) The company works together with about 1,133 farmers that produce milk for Vonpar, and Vonpar provides technical assistance to the farmers it sources raw milk from, with dedicated staff, and will support the farmers in  improving the quality of milk in light of the new milk safety regulations that are expected to come to effect in 2012; and (ii) although the production staffing needs will decline in the new chocolate factory due to increased automation and efficiencies gained from co-locating the candy and chocolate plants, increased employment is expected in the transportation, sales and promotion staff as sales of the company continue to increase.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Vonpar Alimentos S.A. (Vonpar Alimentos or the Company) has an investment program for 2011-2013 to the relocation and expansion of its chocolate manufacturing plant, to be located in the city of Arroio do Meio, Brazil and the expansion and modernization of the Companys dairy and candy businesses.</narrative>
  </description>
